=== db-router-decision.md ===
```yaml
feature: "Surface a Risk Signals strip on the call detail page with badges linking to the cited utterance"
databases:
  bigquery:
    in_scope: false
    reason: "No funnel or activity data is involved; risk signals + utterances are sales-coaching domain."
  neon_savvy_dashboard:
    in_scope: false
    reason: "No Dashboard Prisma tables are touched."
  neon_sales_coaching:
    in_scope: true
    reason: "Call detail page reads call_notes and call_transcripts (utterances) directly via pg; a new risk_signals table would also live here."
preread_paths:
  neon_sales_coaching:
    - .claude/neon-sales-coaching.md
mcp_tools:
  neon_sales_coaching:
    - mcp__Neon__describe_table_schema
```

